# Intelli-Credit — Frontend Architecture Report

> **Project:** Intelli-Credit — AI-Powered Credit Appraisal Platform  
> **Framework:** React 19 + Vite 7  
> **Date:** 2026-03-07

---

## 1. Tech Stack & Dependencies

| Category | Technology | Version |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| **UI Framework** | React | 19.2.4 |
| **Bundler** | Vite | 7.3.1 |
| **Routing** | React Router DOM | 7.13.1 |
| **Animations** | Framer Motion | 12.34.3 |
| **HTTP Client** | Axios | 1.13.6 |
| **Charts** | Recharts | 3.7.0 |
| **Icons** | Lucide React + React Icons | 0.575.0 / 5.5.0 |
| **WebSocket** | STOMP.js + SockJS | 7.3.0 / 1.6.1 |
| **3D Embeds** | Spline (React + Runtime) | 4.1.0 / 1.12.61 |
| **Styling** | Vanilla CSS (per-component CSS files) | — |

