### 7.1 [DashboardLayout](file:///d:/Hackathon%20stuff/IITH-Hackathon/intelli-credit/src/components/DashboardLayout.jsx#13-42)

**Used by:** DataIngestor, ResearchAgent, RecommendationEngine

