### 7.2 [Sidebar](file:///d:/Hackathon%20stuff/IITH-Hackathon/intelli-credit/src/components/Sidebar.jsx#14-72)

Fixed left navigation with 5 items:

| Label | Icon | Links To |
|-------|------|----------|
| Dashboard | LayoutDashboard | `/ingestor` |
| Ingestion | Upload | `/ingestor` |
| Research | Search | `/research` |
| Decisions | Gavel | `/recommendation` |
| Export CAM | FileOutput | `/recommendation` |

- Active item has a spring-animated indicator (Framer Motion `layoutId`)
- Brand: "IC" icon + "Intelli-Credit" + "AI Platform" badge
- Static user avatar: "Alex Morgan — Senior Analyst"

### 7.3 [AgentFeedWidget](file:///d:/Hackathon%20stuff/IITH-Hackathon/intelli-credit/src/components/AgentFeedWidget.jsx#6-70)

A self-contained WebSocket feed display:
- Shows connection status (Connected / Offline) with `Wifi`/`WifiOff` icons
- Lists `agentFeed` items from context with animated entry/exit
- Each item: status dot (color-coded), agent name, status badge, message, timestamp
- Empty state: "Waiting for agent updates…"

### 7.4 [ConnectionStatus](file:///d:/Hackathon%20stuff/IITH-Hackathon/intelli-credit/src/components/ConnectionStatus.jsx#5-20)

Minimal badge in the dashboard header:
- Shows `Wifi + "Live"` when WebSocket connected
- Shows `WifiOff + "Offline"` when disconnected
- Hidden when no `applicationId` exists

