## 8. Data Flow Summary

```
┌──────────────┐    Form Submit     ┌────────────────────┐
│  DataIngestor │ ─────────────────▶ │  POST /api/app     │
│  (Step 1)     │                    │  → returns appId   │
│               │ ◀──── response ─── └────────────────────┘
│               │                    ┌────────────────────┐
│               │ ─── File Upload ──▶│  POST /api/files   │
│               │                    │  (multipart)       │
└──────┬───────┘                    └────────────────────┘
       │ appId stored in Context + sessionStorage
       │
       │ WebSocket auto-connects to /ws
       │ Subscribes to /topic/agent-updates
       ▼
┌──────────────┐    Officer Note    ┌────────────────────┐
│ ResearchAgent │ ─────────────────▶│  POST .../notes    │
│  (Step 2)     │    PD Transcript ─▶│  POST .../pd       │
│               │    Stress Test ───▶│  POST .../stress   │
│               │                    └────────────────────┘
│               │ ◀── WebSocket ─── agent status updates
└──────┬───────┘
       │ Context auto-refreshes on agent 'completed' status
       ▼
┌──────────────────┐  GET /api/app/{id}  ┌────────────────┐
│ RecommendationEng│ ──────────────────▶ │  Backend       │
│  (Step 3)         │ ◀── ucsoData ──── │  (full UCSO)   │
│                   │                    └────────────────┘
│  Renders:         │
│  - Credit Score   │
│  - SHAP values    │
│  - Charts         │
│  - CAM Report gen │
└──────────────────┘
```

---

## 9. UCSO Data Structure (expected from backend)

The frontend reads these nested paths from the `ucsoData` object returned by `GET /api/application/{id}`:

```
ucsoData
├── applicant
│   ├── name, business_name, pan, cin, mobile, email
│   ├── gst_number, loan_amount, loan_type
│   ├── annual_turnover, sector, incorporation_year
│   ├── employee_count, requested_tenure_months
│   └── ... (any additional fields)
├── risk
│   ├── agent_confidence      (float 0–1, used for risk score ring)
│   ├── default_probability   (string: "low" | "medium" | "high")
│   ├── risk_grade            (string: e.g. "A+", "B", "C")
│   └── shap_values           (object: { feature_name: float_contribution, ... })
├── derived_features
│   ├── credit_score          (number, 0–900)
│   ├── cash_flow_score       (number, 0–100)
│   ├── debt_ratio_score      (number, 0–100)
│   ├── market_position_score (number, 0–100)
│   ├── management_score      (number, 0–100)
│   ├── suggested_rate        (number, interest rate %)
│   └── interest_rate         (number, fallback for suggested_rate)
├── financials
│   ├── cash_flow_score       (fallback for derived_features)
│   └── debt_ratio_score      (fallback for derived_features)
├── compliance
│   └── compliance_score      (number, 0–100)
├── human_notes (or notes)
│   └── [ { author, note/text, timestamp }, ... ]
└── ... (other agent namespaces)
```

