## 10. Environment Configuration

**File:** [.env](file:///d:/Hackathon%20stuff/IITH-Hackathon/intelli-credit/.env)

| Variable | Purpose | Default |
|----------|---------|---------|
| `VITE_API_BASE_URL` | Backend API base URL (REST + WebSocket) | `http://localhost:8080` |

WebSocket endpoint is derived as: `{VITE_API_BASE_URL}/ws`

