## 11. Key UX Features

| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|---------------|
| **Page Transitions** | `AnimatePresence` with fade + slide animations between routes |
| **3D Tilt Cards** | CSS `perspective` + JS mouse tracking (landing page) |
| **Cursor Glow** | `motion.div` following cursor with spring physics |
| **Parallax Scrolling** | `useScroll` + `useTransform` on landing hero |
| **Glassmorphism** | `backdrop-filter: blur()` on nav, cards, footer |
| **Animated Risk Ring** | SVG circle `strokeDashoffset` animation |
| **Live Feed Animations** | `AnimatePresence` with staggered entry for feed items |
| **Drag & Drop Upload** | Native HTML5 drag events on document upload slots |
| **Progress Bars** | Real-time Axios `onUploadProgress` callbacks |
| **Session Persistence** | `applicationId` stored in `sessionStorage` to survive page reloads |
| **Auto-refresh** | 30-second polling on Recommendation page when risk data incomplete |
| **Ticker Marquee** | Infinite horizontal CSS animation |
